<text top="555" left="113" width="103" height="13" font="0">Council of 18 June 2007, </text>
<text top="576" left="113" width="2" height="9" font="2"><b> </b></text>
<text top="576" left="142" width="51" height="9" font="5"><i>Underlining </i></text>
<text top="573" left="195" width="74" height="13" font="0">the  importance  of</text>
