<text top="573" left="274" width="210" height="13" font="0">all  General  Assembly  resolutions  on  measures  to </text>
<text top="585" left="113" width="371" height="13" font="0">eliminate  international  terrorism,  including  Assembly  resolutions  46/51  of  9  December </text>
